column2: "Wait! Hadred, don't run away! Damn it!"
"We need to hurry up and chase after him!"
"Don't get in my way! I don't need any medical attention!"
"I have to hurry up and finish off Hadred!"
"... sorry. I let my emotions get the best of me."
"...I can't sense him anywhere. I guess there's nothing that can be done."
